   FBC-GATORNOTES _ Georgia Tech-Notre Dame combined Gator Bowl
notebook. (Rogers, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) 20.
</P>
<P>
   FBC-PEACHNOTES _ ATLANTA _ Georgia-Virginia combined Peach Bowl
notebook. (Schlabach, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 20.
</P>
<P>
   HOCKEY
</P>
<P>
   HKN-FLORIDA-ICE _ The NHL, its players and coaches are
complaining about ice, of all things. Many arenas are having big
problems with their ice, having problems keeping it in condition so
that players are not skatingthrough ruts and injuring themselves
and causing poor, low-scoring play. (Biggane, Palm Beach Post).
MOVED SATURDAY
</P>
