<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-27 18:23 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7657 &Cx1f; tth-z
r d &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-OWEN-FOOD-COLUMN-SPI &LR;      12-27 0873
